title: Mary Earps : England keeper on women football growth since Euros win
body_text:
You can feel how game has grown since Euros win - Earps
England goalkeeper Mary Earps says she can "feel how much the game has grown" since the Lionesses won Euro 2022 and discusses how she feels women's football can improve in the future.
READ MORE: Euros legacy helps 129,000 more girls take up football
